OL,3,CFringe programme launches featuring
OL,4,C'notable increase' in overseas
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,FThe programme for the Edinburgh
OL,8,FFestival Fringe has been launched,
OL,9,Fdetailing 3,649 shows across 258
OL,10,Fvenues.
OL,12,FThis year's event features shows on
OL,13,Ftopics including artificial
OL,14,Fintelligence, the manosphere, cults
OL,15,Fand social class.
OL,17,FThere will be a total of 53,884
OL,18,Fperformances during the Fringe, which
OL,19,Fruns between August 7 and 31.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
