OL,3,CFringe programme launches featuring
OL,4,C'notable increase' in overseas
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,FA total of 935 of the shows are
OL,8,FScottish.
OL,10,FWith performers from 71 countries
OL,11,Frepresented at the Fringe, organisers
OL,12,Fsay there has been a "notable
OL,13,Fincrease" in artists registering from
OL,14,Foverseas.
OL,16,FThe Gilded Balloon Teviot is returning
OL,17,Fto this year's Fringe as a venue after
OL,18,Fthe historic student union building
OL,19,Fwas refurbished.
OL,26,@tD@VOUuD@IO]
