OL,3,CFringe programme launches featuring
OL,4,C'notable increase' in overseas
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,FOther venues include a "sauna theatre"
OL,8,Fat Summerhall and the "pianodrome" `
OL,9,Fan amphitheatre made entirely of
OL,10,Fdisuses pianos.
OL,12,FTony Lankester, chief executive of the
OL,13,FEdinburgh Festival Fringe Society,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Thank-you to the artists,
OL,15,Fvenues, producers, technicians,
OL,16,Fpromoters, support staff and audiences
OL,17,Fthat bring their unique creative lens
OL,18,Fand exceptional energy to Edinburgh
OL,19,Feach August.
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@fO]pD@WOUpD@bO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
