OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780538605
OL,3,CFringe programme launches featuring
OL,4,C'notable increase' in overseas
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,F"Within the number of productions
OL,8,Fregistering this year, we've seen a
OL,9,Fnotable increase in artist
OL,10,Fregistrations from overseas.
OL,12,F"This tells us that, despite the
OL,13,Feconomic and political headwinds the
OL,14,Fworld is facing, the Fringe continues
OL,15,Fto be relevant and important to our
OL,16,Fartists, and taking part marks, for
OL,17,Fthem, a significant moment and
OL,18,Finvestment in their careers.
OL,20,F"This year's Fringe programme is
OL,21,Fpacked with every kind of performance.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU|D@AOU
