CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780538605
OL,3,CFringe programme launches featuring
OL,4,C'notable increase' in overseas
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,F"We're asking audiences to mix it up
OL,8,Fand explore the unique, creative
OL,9,Fperformances available at this Fringe.
OL,11,F"From theatre or circus, or the best
OL,12,Fof comedy, music, dance, children's
OL,13,Fshows, magic or cabaret, there is
OL,14,Fsomething for everyone in Edinburgh
OL,15,Fthis August."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@MO]
